# Superstore Sales Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes the Sample Superstore dataset using Microsoft Power BI.

## KPIs
- Total Sales
- Total Profit
- Sales by Category
- Sales by Segment
- Sales by Region
- Top Products

## Features
- Interactive slicers for Region, Category, and Segment
- KPI Cards
- Bar Charts
- Pie Chart
- Product Analysis

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Power BI
- Sample Superstore Dataset

## Dashboard
Interactive dashboard with filters and business insights.
